{"tid":2365018,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"盈富基金明日恢復投資受制裁股份","createTime":"2021-01-13T12:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T12:53:01.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a608126b711f7228c5d1ecf14803f490ff311809","tid":2365018,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T12:08:44.000Z","msg":"盈富基金的經理人美國道富環球發公告指，盈富基金明日起將恢復對恒生指數成份股的受制裁實體進行投資。<br />\n<br />\n公告重申，盈富基金的投資目標，是提供緊貼恒指表現的投資回報。為達到投資目標，經理人會把盈富基金全部或絕大部分資產，投資於恒指成份股，比重大致上與有關股份佔恒指比重相同。<br />\n<br />\n受行政命令影響，盈富基金將不再適合美國人士投資，投資者應考慮投資盈富基金是否適合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570235-20210113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570235-20210113.htm&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuFCKRJWvDXkpEFRbHtszOvM%3D&h=aef4c9a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570235-20210113.htm&h=f2252307\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570235-20210113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"eb0666d865d39e6c39813adbf916a5ce543bca1f","tid":2365018,"uid":35342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T12:11:52.000Z","msg":"又彈出彈入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e912f3ee14f5bc4315f66639818520264c2803","tid":2365018,"uid":98477,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"拜金贏咗真係乜都夠膽死"},{"pid":"35715f14460eca76c0ed0f79b11fc985a0fce7c8","tid":2365018,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T12:53:01.000Z","msg":"拜登一上台   咩政策 咩規矩都唔駛守了"}]}